OL,3,CMan appears in court accused of stone
OL,4,Ccircle summer solstice event murder
OL,6,FA murder suspect accused of killing a
OL,7,F26-year-old man during a summer
OL,8,Fsolstice event in Derbyshire has been
OL,9,Fremanded in custody until September.
OL,11,FPolish national Szymon Babynko spoke
OL,12,Fonly to confirm his name during a
OL,13,Fbrief hearing at Derby Crown Court on
OL,14,FWednesday, and was told his trial will
OL,15,Ftake place in either November this
OL,16,Fyear or March next year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
