PN,34302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782915514
OL,3,CMan appears in court accused of stone
OL,4,Ccircle summer solstice event murder
OL,6,FThe 23-year-old, appearing by a prison
OL,7,Fvideo-link, is accused of murdering
OL,8,FIsaac Clare-Watts, whose body was
OL,9,Ffound at the Nine Ladies Stone Circle
OL,10,Fin the Peak District on 22 June.
OL,12,FBabynko, of Commonwealth Way, London,
OL,13,Fhas also been charged with attempted
OL,14,Fmurder in relation to an incident in
OL,15,FHady Lane, Chesterfield, on 25 June.
OL,17,FHe was not required to enter a plea to
OL,18,Feither charge during his appearance
OL,19,Fbefore Judge Shaun Smith KC and was
OL,20,Fordered to reappear for a plea hearing
OL,21,Fon 25 September.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782915514
OL,3,CMan appears in court accused of stone
OL,4,Ccircle summer solstice event murder
OL,6,FAdjourning the case, the judge told
OL,7,Fthe defendant: "Mr Babynko, there is
OL,8,Fgoing to be a trial in this case at
OL,9,Fsome stage.
OL,11,F"It may be in November but it's more
OL,12,Flikely to be in March next year.
OL,14,F"In the meantime, you are remanded in
OL,15,Fcustody.
OL,17,F"At the next hearing you are going to
OL,18,Fappear over the link, when we are
OL,19,Fgoing to see how far people have got
OL,20,Fin preparing the case.
OL,26,@oD@POUsD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU
